title: Touch on
description: Chiho has been unlucky his whole life, but he was actually born with a rare, most auspicious destiny. It’s just that his mother, who is a shaman, decided to share his energies with seven girls in their neighborhood to help them overcome their cursed fates. But now that Chiho has become an adult, it’s time for him to retrieve his energies. And the way to do that is… through touch?! A new comic from the creators of Ms. Mystic.
